                            <comment id="12539496" author="hossman" created="Fri, 2 Nov 2007 01:00:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch that takes the previous proof of concept and integrates it into the solr build.xml as a new &quot;stub-factories&quot; target.&lt;/p&gt;

